          <a href="https://vellum.ai/llm-leaderboard" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent,#2D8ABF);">Vellum</a> and
          <a href="https://onyx.app/llm-leaderboard" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent,#2D8ABF);">Onyx</a> leaderboards as of March 2026.
          No single benchmark captures true capability; the vertical axis reflects a rough consensus across sources, not a precise measurement.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
          <strong style="color:var(--text-sec,#3D4455);">Cost scores</strong> are based on blended API token pricing (input + output at an approximate 3:1 ratio) from official provider documentation and
