          <strong style="color:var(--text-sec,#3D4455);">This chart is pedagogical, not a buying guide.</strong> It illustrates the structure of the cost-capability landscape (the frontier, the open/closed divide, the clustering patterns). Positions are approximate and will shift as new models release and prices change. Always check current data before committing to a model for a research project.
        </p>
